<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所謂的復活節啊，<delay8 />
就是要開心地在島上尋找蛋！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你收集多少了啊——？<pageBreak /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />蛋的種類有很多，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要全部收集到的話，可要有十足的幹勁！<delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay8 />加油吧——！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿，<delay8 />你已經見過<delay20 />
廣場上的<colour id="3" />蹦蹦<colour id="65535" />了嗎——？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那傢伙，<delay8 />無論什麼時候都在跳，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你別小看他，那樣可是相當辛苦的。<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />他有時候會嘆超大一口氣啊——！</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好了嗎？！<delay8 />復活節這一天啊，<delay20 />
就是要來測試平常鍛鍊的成果！<pageBreak /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />搖晃樹木、挖掘地面<tag a="110" b="0" />等等，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />辛苦程度<delay8 />絕不輸給鐵人三項咧！<delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />打起精神，加油好嗎——？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也是聽人家說的啦，<delay frames="30" />
聽說使用哩數旅行券前往的那座無人島上，
會有蛋<delay8 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />掉落在岩石附近喔！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很奇怪對吧——？<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />岩石生蛋這件事，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺有點浪漫啊——！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />馬上就要到復活節了！<delay frames="30" />
你<delay8 />準備好了嗎——？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說到復活節一定會想到蛋！<delay frames="30" />
雖然到處都撿得到蛋，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我還是最推薦<delay8 />可疑的椰子樹喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯？<delay8 />你果然不相信啊？<delay40 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈，<delay8 />要是找到的話，
就敲敲看吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年的復活節是在<tag a="90" b="35" arg="0xcd00" />月<tag a="90" b="36" arg="0xcd00" />日喔！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我<delay8 />超級期待的——！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在復活節正式來臨之前，努力尋找島上的蛋<delay20 />
應該是很好的健身活動，肌肉也會變結實吧？<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喔～！<delay8 />我的鬥志燃燒了——！！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你最近<delay20 />有釣到
大約中型尺寸的魚嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我前幾天做夢<delay8 />想要釣這種尺寸的魚，<delay20 />
結果不知道為什麼總是釣到蛋。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓人有點好奇，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>